'''Croatian Interdisciplinary Society''' ({{lang-hr|Hrvatsko interdisciplinarno društvo}}, abbrev. ''HID'') is a [[non-governmental organization]] operating in [[Croatia]]. It acts to promote [[interdisciplinary]] [[education]] and [[research]], primarily but not exclusively in the domain of [[complex systems]]. They are a member society of the [[International Federation for Systems Research]].
