'''''Geometriae Dedicata''''' is a [[mathematical journal]], founded in 1972, concentrating on [[geometry]] and its relationship to [[topology]], [[group theory]] and the theory of [[dynamical system]]s. It was created on the initiative of [[Hans Freudenthal]] in [[Utrecht (city)|Utrecht]], the [[Netherlands]].<ref name="80bday">{{citation|journal=Geometriae Dedicata|year=1985|volume=19|issue=1|pages=3–5|title=In honor of Hans Freudenthal on his eightieth birthday|first=F. D.|last=Veldkamp|doi=10.1007/BF00233100}}.</ref> It is published by [[Springer Verlag|Springer]] Netherlands. The [[Editor-in-Chief|Editors-in-Chief]] are John R. Parker and Jean-Marc Schlenker.<ref>Journal website</ref>

